Lists all the assets/files in a given volume.

Source: R/list_assets_in_volume.R
list_assets_in_volume.Rd

Lists all the assets/files in a given volume.

list_assets_in_volume(vol_id = 1, vb = FALSE)

Arguments

vol_id

Target volume number.
vb

A boolean value.

Value

List of assets.

Examples

list_assets_in_volume()
